text: Andrei Olegovich Timofeyev (; born 8 February 1996) is a Russian football player who plays as a goalkeeper. ==Club career== He made his debut in the Russian Premier League for FC Ural Yekaterinburg on 29 April 2017 in a game against FC Terek Grozny. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:People from Ivdel Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:FC Ural Yekaterinburg players Category:Russian Premier League players Category:Association football goalkeepers
